OL,3,CMan offered hot chocolate to girl
OL,4,Cbefore trying to abduct her, court told
OL,6,FA man who allegedly tried to entice a
OL,7,F12-year-old girl into his car by
OL,8,Foffering her a hot chocolate, has been
OL,9,Fremanded in custody.
OL,11,FThe judge at Belfast Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt said cases like this "send
OL,13,Fshivers down the spine of any parent".
OL,15,FPaul Laird from Gracehill in Ballymena
OL,16,Ffaces charges of and denies stalking
OL,17,Fand child abduction over two separate
OL,18,Fapproaches in Whitehead in Co Antrim.
OL,20,FThe 58-year-old allegedly approached
OL,21,Fthe girl last week.
