OL,3,CMan offered hot chocolate to girl
OL,4,Cbefore trying to abduct her, court told
OL,6,FThe court heard how the first alleged
OL,7,Fencounter was at a convenience store
OL,8,Fin the coastal town.
OL,10,FThe investigating detective told the
OL,11,Fcourt Laird approached her twice in
OL,12,Fthe shop and asked about her fitness
OL,13,Fand where she went to school.
OL,15,FThe following evening, the defendant
OL,16,Fallegedly pulled up his car alongside
OL,17,Fher while she was out walking.
OL,19,FThe detective said Laird asked the
OL,20,Fgirl if she wanted to get into the car
OL,21,Fand go for a hot chocolate.
