OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773349950
OL,3,CMan offered hot chocolate to girl
OL,4,Cbefore trying to abduct her, court told
OL,6,FAfter declining his request, Laird
OL,7,Fallegedly persisted up to six times
OL,8,Fbefore driving off.
OL,10,FThe court heard how the 12-year-old
OL,11,Fburst into tears and called her mum to
OL,12,Fcome and collect her.
OL,14,FDuring police interviews, the
OL,15,Fdefendant said he realised the girl
OL,16,Fwas scared "by the look on her face"
OL,17,Fand that he had "made a mistake".
OL,19,FHe added: "That frightened him and he
OL,20,Fdrove off."
