PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773349950
OL,3,CMan offered hot chocolate to girl
OL,4,Cbefore trying to abduct her, court told
OL,6,FLaird denied trying to abduct the girl
OL,7,For being sexually attracted to
OL,8,Fchildren.
OL,10,FThe judge refused bail stating "this
OL,11,Fis the type of case that sends shivers
OL,12,Fdown the spine of any parent".
OL,14,FLaird was remanded in custody to
OL,15,Fappear before court again in April.
